				<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><a class="a2a_button_facebook" href="https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/facebook?linkurl=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dentacoin.com%2Fblog%2Fdentacoin-international-scientific-practical-conference-digital-economy-perm-russia%2F&amp;linkname=Dentacoin%20Participated%20in%20the%207th%20International%20Scientific-Practical%20Conference%20%E2%80%9CDigital%20Economy%E2%80%9D%20in%20Perm%2C%20Russia" title="Facebook" rel="nofollow" target="_blank"></a><a class="a2a_button_twitter" href="https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/twitter?linkurl=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dentacoin.com%2Fblog%2Fdentacoin-international-scientific-practical-conference-digital-economy-perm-russia%2F&amp;linkname=Dentacoin%20Participated%20in%20the%207th%20International%20Scientific-Practical%20Conference%20%E2%80%9CDigital%20Economy%E2%80%9D%20in%20Perm%2C%20Russia" title="Twitter" rel="nofollow" target="_blank"></a><a class="a2a_button_google_plus" href="https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/google_plus?linkurl=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dentacoin.com%2Fblog%2Fdentacoin-international-scientific-practical-conference-digital-economy-perm-russia%2F&amp;linkname=Dentacoin%20Participated%20in%20the%207th%20International%20Scientific-Practical%20Conference%20%E2%80%9CDigital%20Economy%E2%80%9D%20in%20Perm%2C%20Russia" title="Google+" rel="nofollow" target="_blank"></a><a class="a2a_button_reddit" href="https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/reddit?linkurl=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dentacoin.com%2Fblog%2Fdentacoin-international-scientific-practical-conference-digital-economy-perm-russia%2F&amp;linkname=Dentacoin%20Participated%20in%20the%207th%20International%20Scientific-Practical%20Conference%20%E2%80%9CDigital%20Economy%E2%80%9D%20in%20Perm%2C%20Russia" title="Reddit" rel="nofollow" target="_blank"></a><a class="a2a_button_whatsapp" href="https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/whatsapp?linkurl=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dentacoin.com%2Fblog%2Fdentacoin-international-scientific-practical-conference-digital-economy-perm-russia%2F&amp;linkname=Dentacoin%20Participated%20in%20the%207th%20International%20Scientific-Practical%20Conference%20%E2%80%9CDigital%20Economy%E2%80%9D%20in%20Perm%2C%20Russia" title="WhatsApp" rel="nofollow" target="_blank"></a><a class="a2a_button_linkedin" href="https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/linkedin?linkurl=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dentacoin.com%2Fblog%2Fdentacoin-international-scientific-practical-conference-digital-economy-perm-russia%2F&amp;linkname=Dentacoin%20Participated%20in%20the%207th%20International%20Scientific-Practical%20Conference%20%E2%80%9CDigital%20Economy%E2%80%9D%20in%20Perm%2C%20Russia" title="LinkedIn" rel="nofollow" target="_blank"></a><a class="a2a_button_email" href="https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/email?linkurl=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dentacoin.com%2Fblog%2Fdentacoin-international-scientific-practical-conference-digital-economy-perm-russia%2F&amp;linkname=Dentacoin%20Participated%20in%20the%207th%20International%20Scientific-Practical%20Conference%20%E2%80%9CDigital%20Economy%E2%80%9D%20in%20Perm%2C%20Russia" title="Email" rel="nofollow" target="_blank"></a><a class="a2a_dd a2a_counter addtoany_share_save" href="https://www.addtoany.com/share#url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dentacoin.com%2Fblog%2Fdentacoin-international-scientific-practical-conference-digital-economy-perm-russia%2F&amp;title=Dentacoin%20Participated%20in%20the%207th%20International%20Scientific-Practical%20Conference%20%E2%80%9CDigital%20Economy%E2%80%9D%20in%20Perm%2C%20Russia" data-a2a-url="https://www.dentacoin.com/blog/dentacoin-international-scientific-practical-conference-digital-economy-perm-russia/" data-a2a-title="Dentacoin Participated in the 7th International Scientific-Practical Conference “Digital Economy” in Perm, Russia"></a></p><p><strong>On November 21<sup>st</sup> -22<sup>nd</sup> the Founder of Dentacoin Prof. Dimitar Dimitrakiev, PhD and our Co-Founder and Core Developer Jeremias Grenzebach attended the <a href="http://sr.pstu.ru/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">7<sup>th</sup> International Scientific-Practical Conference “Digital Economy: New Competences, Organizations and Governance”</a> held in Perm State National Research University, Russia.</strong></p>
<div id="attachment_1269" style="width: 260px" class="wp-caption alignleft"><a href="https://www.dentacoin.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/Jeremias-Grenzebach-Dentacoin-Perm-Conference.-Russia.jpg" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><img class="wp-image-1269" src="https://www.dentacoin.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/Jeremias-Grenzebach-Dentacoin-Perm-Conference.-Russia-300x210.jpg" alt="Jeremias Grenzebach, Dentacoin - Perm Conference. Russia" width="250" height="175" srcset="https://www.dentacoin.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/Jeremias-Grenzebach-Dentacoin-Perm-Conference.-Russia-300x210.jpg 300w, https://www.dentacoin.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/Jeremias-Grenzebach-Dentacoin-Perm-Conference.-Russia-768x538.jpg 768w, https://www.dentacoin.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/Jeremias-Grenzebach-Dentacoin-Perm-Conference.-Russia-1024x717.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 250px) 100vw, 250px" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">Jeremias Grenzebach, Core Developer at Dentacoin on the topic &#8220;Blockchain: from Genesis to DAO&#8221;</p></div>
<p>The conference is a highly respected event, initiated by the Perm Government, the Institute of Economics, the Ural Branch of Russian Academy of Sciences, Perm State National Research University, International Joseph A. Schumpeter Society and Russian Association of Business Education.</p>
<p>The event was also attended by leading professors at technical universities from all over Russia, Rostelecom – the leading telecommunication company in Russia, which is building a Smart City Project in the Astrakhan region, as well as many representatives from different business sectors.</p>
<p>Dentacoin Foundation, as a pioneering organization in industry-centric Blockchain technology solutions, was identified as a perfect example to represent<a href="https://www.dentacoin.com/blog/report-initial-effects-using-dentacoin-f3t-dental-clinic-london/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"> how Blockchain advantages can be utilized for bringing efficiencies in an entire industry</a>. Prof. Dimitrakiev introduced the Dentacoin concept, and Jeremias Grenzebach’s speech was on the topic of “Blockchain &#8211; from Genesis to DAO”. Both presentations were followed by active discussions and questions from the audience. Video coming soon.</p>
<p>Undoubtedly, the topic of Blockchain is gaining enormous popularity around the world and therefore many leading companies are looking for great examples of how to apply Blockchain solutions to innovative projects. Such is the case of the Russian Telecommunication Giant Rostelecom, which has just finished the first stage of the innovative project “Smart City” concept and implemented a photo and video surveillance system to record driving violations and strengthen control over the movement of heavy and large vehicles in the Astrakhan region.</p>
<div id="attachment_1282" style="width: 260px" class="wp-caption alignright"><a href="https://www.dentacoin.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/Prof.-Dimitrakiev-Dentacoin-Perm-Conference-Russia.jpg" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><img class="wp-image-1282" src="https://www.dentacoin.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/Prof.-Dimitrakiev-Dentacoin-Perm-Conference-Russia-300x210.jpg" alt="Prof. Dimitar Dimitrakiev, Dentacoin - Perm Conference, Russia" width="250" height="175" srcset="https://www.dentacoin.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/Prof.-Dimitrakiev-Dentacoin-Perm-Conference-Russia-300x210.jpg 300w, https://www.dentacoin.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/Prof.-Dimitrakiev-Dentacoin-Perm-Conference-Russia-768x538.jpg 768w, https://www.dentacoin.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/Prof.-Dimitrakiev-Dentacoin-Perm-Conference-Russia-1024x717.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 250px) 100vw, 250px" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">Prof. Dimitar Dimitrakiev presenting the Dentacoin concept</p></div>
<p>As a major resolution from the conference emerged the need for a following conference, under the patronage of Dentacoin Foundation and Prof. Dr. Dimitrakiev in the city of Varna, Bulgaria, where the professor works and lives. Dentacoin will host the conference, which will conclude in an intensive training of a number of academic professionals on the topic of Blockchain, as well as in a more detailed examination of the Dentacoin concept and its real-world application and impact on the dental industry. The introduction to Blockchain Studies in the Academic Calendar is a priority for many technical universities in the Russian Federation and it’s an honor for us to support this initiative.</p>
<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.dentacoin.com/blog/dentacoin-international-scientific-practical-conference-digital-economy-perm-russia/">Dentacoin Participated in the 7th International Scientific-Practical Conference “Digital Economy” in Perm, Russia</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.dentacoin.com/blog">Dentacoin blog</a>.</p>
]]></content:encoded>
